{"word":"δάκρυ","slug":"δάκρυ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δάκρυ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic for <a href='S:δάκρυον'><el>δάκρυον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a tear</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>lacruma</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>δάκρυον</el>, any <i>drop</i>, <el>δ. πεύκινον</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}